### 新增一个多季多部分示例作品
POST http://localhost:8080/api/subjects
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "titleCn": "进击的巨人",
  "subtitle": "The Final Season Part 1",
  "displayTitle": "进击的巨人 The Final Season Part 1",
  "seasonIndex": 4,
  "partIndex": 1,
  "coverUrl": "https://example.com/aot-final-part1.jpg",
  "summary": "用于测试的最终季前半部分示例数据",
  "releaseYear": 2020,
  "releaseMonth": 12,
  "category": "ANIME",
  "studioName": "MAPPA",
  "platformLink": "https://bgm.tv/subject/example",
  "status": "NORMAL"
}

### 新增一个不带季和部分的普通作品
POST http://localhost:8080/api/subjects
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "titleCn": "孤独摇滚！",
  "displayTitle": "孤独摇滚！",
  "coverUrl": "https://example.com/bocchi.jpg",
  "summary": "用于测试的普通单作品示例数据",
  "releaseYear": 2022,
  "releaseMonth": 10,
  "category": "ANIME",
  "studioName": "CloverWorks",
  "platformLink": "https://bgm.tv/subject/example2",
  "status": "NORMAL"
}

### 查询全部作品
GET http://localhost:8080/api/subjects

### 按主类型查询作品
GET http://localhost:8080/api/subjects?category=ANIME

### 按 id 查询作品
GET http://localhost:8080/api/subjects/1

### 按 id 更新作品
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/subjects/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "titleCn": "进击的巨人",
  "subtitle": "The Final Season Part 2",
  "displayTitle": "进击的巨人 The Final Season Part 2",
  "seasonIndex": 4,
  "partIndex": 2,
  "coverUrl": "https://example.com/aot-final-part2.jpg",
  "summary": "用于测试的最终季后半部分示例数据",
  "releaseYear": 2021,
  "releaseMonth": 1,
  "category": "ANIME",
  "studioName": "MAPPA",
  "platformLink": "https://bgm.tv/subject/example-updated",
  "status": "NORMAL"
}

### 删除一个未被引用的作品
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/subjects/2

### 删除一个已被引用的作品
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/subjects/1

### 按关键词搜索作品
GET http://localhost:8080/api/subjects?keyword=巨人

### 按关键词搜索 Final
GET http://localhost:8080/api/subjects?keyword=Final

### 按类型 + 关键词搜索
GET http://localhost:8080/api/subjects?category=ANIME&keyword=Final
